[
    {
        "start": 0.0,
        "end": 5.96,
        "text": "The biggest lesson on how to handle stress in my life, given as a boon to me before the first shot of rocketry,",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 6.02,
        "end": 9.08,
        "text": "because I was so nervous, I felt sort of like what Arjuna felt.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 9.18,
        "end": 11.34,
        "text": "How are you going to do this? You know, this is ridiculous.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": true
    },
    {
        "start": 11.5,
        "end": 13.18,
        "text": "You never called action or cut in your life.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 13.46,
        "end": 16.2,
        "text": "Some friend of mine called and I was ready to give up.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 16.32,
        "end": 17.8,
        "text": "I mean, he said, Maddy, you're already there, man.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 17.86,
        "end": 19.36,
        "text": "You know, what are you going to lose? Put the camera.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": true
    },
    {
        "start": 19.48,
        "end": 20.74,
        "text": "Just take one shot.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 20.88,
        "end": 23.56,
        "text": "If you think you're still not getting it, cancel it after the end of the day.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 23.64,
        "end": 24.48,
        "text": "But take your first shot.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 24.62,
        "end": 25.8,
        "text": "And I said, you know what? OK, right.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": true
    },
    {
        "start": 25.92,
        "end": 26.84,
        "text": "That makes a lot more sense.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 27.12,
        "end": 28.4,
        "text": "And then we took my first shot.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 28.4,
        "end": 34.08,
        "text": "And as I took the shot, I saw it being a complete replication of what I had envisaged when I wrote that scene.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 34.2,
        "end": 35.24,
        "text": "That was exactly it.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 35.34,
        "end": 36.36,
        "text": "Biggest lesson in stress.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    },
    {
        "start": 36.54,
        "end": 37.38,
        "text": "One step at a time.",
        "pause_after": false,
        "tonal_change": false
    }
]